    narr:narration """This hub tracks the evolution of resonance-scoring across narrative artifacts, consistently validating the power of [figurative grounding](narr:RubricAssess_Resonance) to bridge technical complexity and human pain. The trajectory moves from high-level [founding-story proof](narr:Rubric_Resonance_YC_Call) and [foundational analogies](narr:Assessment_Resonance_YC) toward increasingly granular [customer-centric scenarios](narr:Rubric_Resonance_CustomerArchitect). While early assessments favored [broad metaphors](narr:Rubric_Resonance_FounderBetaUser) like 'Gods of Olympus' or 'Matrix chips' ([Rubric_Assess_Resonance](narr:Rubric_Assess_Resonance)), recent entries emphasize [concrete operational friction](narr:RubricAssess_Resonance_GTM) and [comparative framing](narr:Rubric_Resonance_YCDemoBeats) (WITH-vs-WITHOUT). The thematic span remains anchored in the tension between abstract 'dream bigger' slogans and the [visceral reality of failure modes](narr:Rubric_Resonance_CustomerArchitect), with [steering-vector metaphors](narr:Rubric_Resonance_ScarletDame) and [shared-memory analogies](narr:RubricAssess_Resonance_WeeklyCall) serving as the primary vehicles for maintaining narrative coherence across diverse audiences.""" ;
